OpenSSL

Support ChaCha20+Poly1305 cipher suites.
For Debian/Ubuntu packages.

How to make packages:

*Debian 7.5 (wheezy)
  (in some directory)
  apt-get -d source openssl
  tar xzf openssl_1.0.1e.orig.tar.gz
  cd openssl-1.0.1e
  tar xzf ../openssl_1.0.1e-2+deb7u9.debian.tar.gz
  cp -a (this repository)/wheezy/debian/* debian/
  debuild -uc -us

*Ubuntu 12.04 LTS (Precise Pangolin)
  (in some directory)
  apt-get -d source openssl
  tar xzf openssl_1.0.1.orig.tar.gz
  cd openssl-1.0.1
  tar xzf ../openssl_1.0.1-4ubuntu5.13.debian.tar.gz
  cp -a (this repository)/precise/debian/* debian/
  debuild -uc -us

